01:32:57,040 --> 01:32:57,760
Hrvatska riječ.

779
01:32:59,040 --> 01:33:00,640
Evo, to ćemo sada za uvodu u ovaj.

780
01:33:01,440 --> 01:33:02,000
Potkastaviti.

781
01:33:02,080 --> 01:33:02,480
Čevitost.

782
